{"tid":1682413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推到有人搞「還我被選權」遊行集會(民陣Gphone入一入黎)","createTime":"2019-10-30T04:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T07:22:44.000Z","uid":285194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bd12768b4b77c4698c29cd620999359f26eb896","tid":1682413,"uid":285194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:45:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">選舉權(包括被選權)喺公民社會基本人權之一</span><br />\n由2016年陳浩天被DQ開始，港共政府一而再再而三基於政見而褫奪香港市民參選權<br />\n明顯違反香港作為公民社會基本人權要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懇請大組織/知名人士(e.g.民陣、gphone本人)入紙申請未來遊行集會活動，要求港共政府承諾以後永久不會因政見而DQ並即時實行雙普選(以及其他訴求)，其餘情況(如提名人數不足、資料缺失等)則保留現有DQ制度<br />\n<br />\n基於港共政府往績，於遊行集會後強烈建議十八區各區居民佔用區內某一商場(e.g.沙田新城市)進行「和你傾」活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以展示區內對唔同事嘅意見，再要求區議會按照民意進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時訓練論政能力同風氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP牌仔冇得推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c8a3a81e91f85ffdd542f33c2b5d51817e3c26","tid":1682413,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:45:58.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4734729de888e92d3143d7e5a262bb6b085d42","tid":1682413,"uid":285194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c8a3a81e91f85ffdd542f33c2b5d51817e3c26","tid":1682413,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:45:58.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a 